prodNameC: 常盈游離甲狀腺素放射免疫試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
Coated tubes for the binding of the ligand: 2 x 50 tubes
125I-labeled monoclonal antibody: one 45 mL vial
The vial contains 310 kBq of 125I-Iabeled immunoglobulins in liquid form with bovine serum albumin, sodium azide (<0.1%) and a dye.
Calibrators: five 0.5 mL vials
The calibrator vials contain T4 in human serum and sodium azide (<0.1%).
Ligand: one 12 mL vial
The vial contains a ligand solution which includes also bovine proteins and sodium azide (<0.1%).
Control serum: one vial
The vial contains T4 in human serum
applicantName: 常盈實業股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市北投區永興路一段49號
efficacy: 游離甲狀腺素在人血清和血漿內的放射免疫測定。
